Katainen Says Collateral Model Is ‘Workable’ for Future Also

-- B y   K a t i   P o h j a n p a l o
-- 
2011-10-04T10:06:40Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-04/katainen-says-collateral-model-is-workable-for-future-also.html
Finnish Prime Minister  Jyrki Katainen 
said the collateral model agreed on yesterday is “workable”
for use in potential future bailouts.  Collateral use may have country-specific differences
depending on which country may request bailout help, he told
reporters in Helsinki today. Finland has insisted on collateral
in exchange for any future bailouts.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Kati Pohjanpalo at 
 kpohjanpalo@bloomberg.net  